      skos:note "Strategic decision memo register with embedded verbatim blockquotes from Scarlet. Mixed register: structured markdown with bold principle headers (memo genre) vs. lowercase first-person in blockquoted speech. Antithesis-heavy structure (navigate vs. embed, reasoning vs. pre-fetch, live vs. cached, incremental vs. wholesale). Active voice dominant in editorial prose. Jargon density moderate — product terms (task-265, task-269, EMPTY_SPARQL, digest, umbrellas, long-context path, Clojure compile) used without definition, implying internal audience. Short punchy declaratives at conviction peaks. Consistent with Scarlet session-memo idiolect." ;
